sections.heading: Sections; supplemental to other laws
sections.text: Sections 60-501 to 60-569 shall in no respect be considered as a repeal of the state motor vehicle law, but shall be construed as supplemental thereto.SourceLaws 1949, c. 178, ยง 65, p. 503.
